      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "**Eligibility** \n\n1. Only Scheduled Caste Girls Students are eligible.\n1. For Diploma level courses, In Std: 10 or 12 should have 50% or more percentile in the examination.\n1. For Graduate level courses, In Std: 12 should have 50% or more percentile in the examination.\n1. Must full fill all conditions of the Government of India&#39;s Post Matric Scholarship Scheme Guidelines.\n1. Income Limit: More than 2.50 Lakh.\n\n",
